(1901, 243, 'advantage_0_about', 'From sketches and interface design, to responsive front-end coding and back-end CMS, we are able to offer you a full-service approach. Our unique vision is that designers and developers should operate under one roof and combine their efforts in order to craft a singular user experience.\r\n<h2>Our UX Design Process</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>Business Analysis:</strong> Idea, Requirement, Consulting.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Research:</strong> Goal Analysis, Workflows, Roadmap.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>IA &amp; Wireframe:</strong> Information Architecture, Layouts, Clickable Prototypes.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>UI (Look and Feel):</strong> Branding, Unique &amp; Recognizable Appearance.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Development:</strong> Front-End, Back-End, Coding.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>User Testing:</strong> Quality Control, Bug, Performance.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Go Live:</strong> Release, Integration Support.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Maintenance:</strong> Enhancement, Update, Warranty.</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1902, 243, '_advantage_0_about', 'field_5b90ada17e62f'),
